HEADWORD: Rhysimeter
<hw>Rhy*sim"e*ter</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/<?/<?/
flow + <ets>-meter</ets>.]</ety> <def>An instrument, acting on the
